             <span>
              <img alt="Peter Lanzani Bosques" src="/argentina/ReSizes/Tiny/Global/argentina/2016/8/crimen/lanzani/GPA_5456.jpg" style="border-width:0px;" title="Peter Lanzani Bosques"/>
             </span>
